OL,3,CSoap workshops helping keep recovering
OL,4,Caddicts and community clean
OL,6,FA Leeds charity is 'cleaning up' the
OL,7,Fcity by carrying out community
OL,8,Fprojects funded by the sale of soaps
OL,9,Fmade in its workshops.
OL,11,FGetting Clean started as a volunteer
OL,12,Fproject in November 2021, formed by
OL,13,Frecovering addicts helping each other
OL,14,Fand the local community to overcome
OL,15,Faddictions.
OL,17,FIt also provides peer-to-peer support
OL,18,Fto people in drug and alcohol recovery.
