OL,3,CSoap workshops helping keep recovering
OL,4,Caddicts and community clean
OL,6,F"We started out with community
OL,7,Fprojects like litter picking, repairs
OL,8,Fand recycling, but we wanted to create
OL,9,Fa product which could fund those
OL,10,Fprojects but also has value in what we
OL,11,Fdo. That's how Soap with Hope was
OL,12,Fborn."
OL,14,FThe soap making sessions are proving
OL,15,Fbeneficial for the members and attract
OL,16,F10 to 20 people per session.
OL,18,FRoss started drinking and taking drugs
OL,19,Fin his teens and said the workshops,
OL,20,Fand the support from others, has
OL,21,Fhelped him on his road to recovery.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/6
