OL,3,CSoap workshops helping keep recovering
OL,4,Caddicts and community clean
OL,6,F"Addiction itself is very isolating
OL,7,Fand it can keep you locked in your own
OL,8,Fhead," he said. "Having the activities
OL,9,Fand sessions like this, it gives me
OL,10,Fthe chance to socialise with people.
OL,11,FFor me, it's all about building
OL,12,Fconnections."
OL,14,FMoney raised through selling the soap
OL,15,Fin stalls across Leeds goes back into
OL,16,Fthe charity to help fund projects for
OL,17,Fthe community.
