OL,4,Caddicts and community clean
OL,6,FThe charity carried out a community
OL,7,Fclean up in an area highlighted as
OL,8,Fhaving antisocial behaviour and drug
OL,9,Fmisuse. Service users cleared the area
OL,10,Fof paraphernalia and rubbish.
OL,12,FClaire lives on the estate and said
OL,13,Fbefore the clean up, she would feel
OL,14,Ftoo afraid to leave her own home.
OL,16,FShe said: "Me and my daughter don't go
OL,17,Fout after dark. Even during the day I
OL,18,Fkeep the doors locked. With all the
OL,19,Fantisocial behaviour that's going on,
OL,20,FI don't like to let her out at night
OL,21,Fbecause I'm scared for her."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/6
