OL,3,CSoap workshops helping keep recovering
OL,4,Caddicts and community clean
OL,6,FFor Chris and the charity, it's an
OL,7,Fopportunity to show that people with
OL,8,Faddictions can give back.
OL,10,F"To see people coming in that are
OL,11,Fcoming form a background of lived
OL,12,Fexperience and giving back to the
OL,13,Fcommunity is massive", he said.
OL,15,F"It helps people look past the
OL,16,Fantisocial aspects of addiction and
OL,17,Fchallenges the stigma. We carry that
OL,18,Fmessage of hope in one big clean
OL,19,Fcycle."
